"to put the [QuickOutlineFragment2]({{site.src.xtext_core}}/org.eclipse.xtext.x"
"text.generator/src/org/eclipse/xtext/xtext/generator/ui/outline/QuickOutlineFr"
"agment2.xtend) into your workflow."
